    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed and six were scoped as not required at MRL 2. The majority of assessed factors meet or exceed required levels, and the model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The overall assessment supports a Medium assurance level consistent with MRL 2 and the available evidence base.",
